name: I'm Lazy
description:
you said, "please,get up!"
i said, "can't get up!"
you said, "please,get up!"
i said, "can't get up!"

This is a lyrical piece from shame-march day.
From this lyric piece reminds when laziness comes to you and all
Stop in place.  Wondering if there's a solution to keep going hand in hand
with laziness. Can technology help? Maybe I want to replace
Some parts of my body became machines.

NB: As long as I'm in control of my consciousness
